title: Swimming Pool, Dishwasher, Wood Style Flooring, Garages Available
posting_body: Welcome Home to Spinnaker Landing Apartments!
This is a 2 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath, approximately 968 Sq.
Enjoy our well-designed one and two bedroom apartments with wood burning fireplaces, spacious kitchens, private patios and so much more.
Our newly renovated homes offer a modern look with stainless steel appliances, wood style flooring and blinds.
Our convenient location provides easy access to light rail and the freeway but is also close to downtown, shopping and the waterfront.
Amazing amenities, outstanding service and a fantastic location makes Spinnaker Landing the perfect place to call home!
Pricing and availability is subject to change.
Please contact our office for details.
$350 pet fee (non refundable) $35 pet rent per pet.
